title: Coronavirus NSW: Two-month-old baby youngest case of COVID-19
description: Coronavirus NSW: Two-month-old baby youngest case of COVID-19 news.com.au
content:
NSW has recorded its first two cases of coronavirus in children aged under 10 including a two-month-old boy.Chief Health Officer Dr Kerry Chant today announced the state’s number of cases had climbed to 1029. That’s a rise of 211 from yesterday.
